  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "33071869-c1ec-4cde-9cac-9e654b609658",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        960,
        -32
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 419,
        "height": 544,
        "content": "## ü§ñ AI Chat Assistant with RAG & Auto-Logging\n\n### How it works\nThis workflow powers an intelligent chat assistant that retrieves context from a Pinecone knowledge base and Google Sheets, responds naturally using OpenAI GPT-5, and logs all conversations automatically. It also includes a weekly email export feature that sends chat history summaries via Gmail.\n\n### Setup steps\n1. **Connect credentials**: OpenAI API, Google Sheets OAuth2, Pinecone API, Google Drive OAuth2, Gmail OAuth2\n2. **Configure Google Sheet**: Update the document ID to point to your conversation log sheet\n3. **Set Pinecone index**: Replace `whatsappchatbot` with your vector database index name\n4. **Test the chat**: Use the chat trigger URL to send a test message\n5. **Upload knowledge**: Add files to the Google Drive folder to auto-index into Pinecone"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "41cffb83-bd63-44cb-8504-a04315ce6025",
